types.description:
Type that represents report location,
e.g.:
{
    "x": 50.123456,
    "y": 30.123456
}

Type to represent a footnote, e.g:
{
    "uuid": "41ae8f0e-d348-44aa-9067-5a56bcc083e5",
    "text": "<p data-block-key="chnrx">Test Footnote Text </p>"
}

Mutation Errors messages and codes mapped to
fields or non fields errors.
Example:
{
    field_name: [
        {
            "message": "error message",
            "code": "error_code"
        }
    ],
    other_field: [
        {
            "message": "error message",
            "code": "error_code"
        }
    ],
    nonFieldErrors: [
        {
            "message": "error message",
            "code": "error_code"
        }
    ]
}
